metadata.name: Melody of Cherry Blossoms
metadata.description:
The sun's radiance upon her bare skin, like the gentle rays filtering through the branches of trees, envelops her. With a gaze both entranced and clear, she absorbs every particle of this enchanting garden within herself. Nestled in the embrace of this garden, she carries the colors and sensations, akin to a vibrant and beautiful flower, showcasing the brilliance of nature.

Her beautiful face gazes pensively into the distance, as if contemplating another world. Does she reminisce about her past in the serenity of the garden? Or is she in search of the hidden secrets that lie within these very surroundings?
